description.en: Jisho is a powerful Japanese-English dictionary. It lets you find words, kanji, example sentences and more quickly and easily.
description.ga_IE: Is Jisho tá cumhachtach Seapáinis-Béarla Foclóir.Ligeann sé duit focail, Kanji, abairtí mar shampla a aimsiú agus níos gasta agus go héasca.
